window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Descend Into Depravity…<br> <br> After the death of his mother, Cade Colter arrives in the seemingly idyllic mountain town of Crimson Cove, where his older brother Brooks is being pulled into the depths of a deadly addiction. His drug of choice: the venom of Gretchen VanTreese, a beautiful, ruthless vampire who rules the Crimson Corset nightclub, a local den of debauchery notorious for its lurid parties and sordid past. <br> <br> As Cade delves into Crimson Cove’s dark underworld to save his brother from a fate far worse than death, he discovers Gretchen’s real obsession: his own blood, which holds the power to create a new breed of vampire that could forever tip the balance between two worlds. <br> <br> Battling against Gretchen’s deadly designs, Cade must confront a terrifying truth: that saving his brother could unleash an unstoppable new world order where Gretchen reigns supreme -- and a vampire uprising could enslave humanity forever.</p>"; 
